commitResults.messageTitle: Category class instances: Remove HashSet storage
commitResults.messageBody:
Previously, more than 1 category was allowed and
data was represented in a HashSet.

Currently, contacts must and can only have 1
Category. It is unnecessary to keep Category in
a HashSet.

Storing contact Category on its own is more
representative of the application.
